            <lg xml:id="TK191">
<l>pallār muṉiyap payaṉila colluvā</l>
<l>ṉellāru meḷḷap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who to the disgust of many speaks useless things will be despised by all.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
